CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Apexigen Inc is a clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company focusing on the discovery and development of innovative antibody-based therapeutics for the treatment of cancer with a focus on immuno-oncology. The company's pipeline of immuno-oncology therapeutic candidates is led by sotigalimab, which is in clinical development, and also includes several preclinical stage immune-oncology programs.
